## ARCHITECTURE CONTEXT

All scanners follow this exact file structure:
- `backend/src/signals/indicators/[name].detect.ts` → Pure detection function (no DB)
- `backend/src/signals/scanners/[name].scanner.ts`  → Fetches candles, calls detect, saves signal
